            <thetext>Element focus should reworked. The whole system needs some more polishing and should be usable more straightforward.

* ComboBoxes should not access protected methods to correctly DOM focus the edit field.
* Focus recatangle should be controllable from appearance - not with a property (enableElementFocus)
* We need a better solution for the outline handling (IE does not support CSS outline)
* Add focus state to all widgets.
* Support for focused/blured areas e.g. lighter focus color when a child is focused in a non-active parent (e.g. focus is in tree while a selection is stored in the listview)
* Maybe solve the whole thing at DOM-level, too</thetext>
